Detailed Description

cvmx_lmc::_mem_cfg1

LMC_MEM_CFG1 = LMC Memory Configuration Register1

This register controls the External Memory Configuration Timing Parameters. Please refer to the appropriate DDR part spec from your memory vendor for the various values in this CSR. The details of each of these timing parameters can be found in the JEDEC spec or the vendor spec of the memory parts.
